import math

def calculate_minimum_moves(n, lst):
    result = []
    prev = 1
    for i in range(n - 1):
        t = int(math.log(n - i - 1, 2))
        prev = prev + lst[i]
        lst[2 ** t + i] += lst[i]
        result.append(prev)
    return result
